claim.claim-text:
An autoinjector (1) comprising:
a case (2) having a hole;
a carrier adapted to hold a syringe (4) and slidably disposed in the case (2);
a cover (8) telescopically coupled to the case (2) and translatable relative to the case (2) between a first position and a second position, wherein in the second position, the cover (8) covers the hole; and
a releasable locking mechanism adapted to lock the cover (8) in the second position.
